HEADWORD: Astonied
<hw>As*ton"ied</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>p. p.</pos> <def>Stunned;
astonished. See <er>Astony</er>.</def> <mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>And I <qex>astonied</qex> fell and could not pray.</q>
<rj><qau>Mrs. Browning.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Astonish</ent>⟦br⟧
